{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "uid": "saleor-tracing",
    "title": "Saleor — Distributed Tracing (Spanmetrics)",
    "description": "Phân tích distributed tracing từ OTel spanmetrics. Slow operations, error hotspots, service breakdown. Jaeger UI: http://localhost:16686",
    "tags": ["saleor", "tracing", "jaeger", "spanmetrics", "thesis"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "editable": true,
    "graphTooltip": 1,
    "liveNow": false,
    "refresh": "15s",
    "schemaVersion": 39,
    "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
    "timepicker": {},
    "version": 1,
    "links": [
      {
        "title": "Open Jaeger UI",
        "url": "http://localhost:16686",
        "type": "link",
        "targetBlank": true,
        "icon": "external link",
        "tooltip": "Mở Jaeger UI để xem trace chi tiết"
      }
    ],
    "templating": {
      "list": [
        {
          "current": {},
          "hide": 0,
          "includeAll": false,
          "multi": false,
          "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
          "options": [],
          "query": "prometheus",
          "refresh": 1,
          "regex": "",
          "skipUrlSync": false,
          "type": "datasource"
        },
        {
          "current": { "selected": false, "text": "All", "value": "$__all" },
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "definition": "label_values(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total, service_name)",
          "hide": 0,
          "includeAll": true,
          "multi": true,
          "name": "service",
          "options": [],
          "query": {
            "query": "label_values(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total, service_name)",
            "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
          },
          "refresh": 2,
          "regex": "",
          "skipUrlSync": false,
          "sort": 1,
          "type": "query",
          "label": "Service"
        }
      ]
    },
    "panels": [

      {
        "collapsed": false,
        "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        "id": 100,
        "title": "📊 Tracing Overview",
        "type": "row"
      },
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Total Spans/s",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
        "transparent": true,
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "sum(rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
            "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "#5794F2", "value": null }] },
            "unit": "reqps", "decimals": 2,
            "mappings": [{ "type": "special", "options": { "match": "null", "result": { "text": "No data" } } }]
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "auto",
          "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Error Spans/s",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 1 },
        "transparent": true,
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "sum(rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "#73BF69", "value": null },
                { "color": "#FF9830", "value": 0.1 },
                { "color": "#F2495C", "value": 1 }
              ]
            },
            "unit": "reqps", "decimals": 3,
            "mappings": [{ "type": "special", "options": { "match": "null", "result": { "text": "0" } } }]
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "auto",
          "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Overall P95 Latency",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 1 },
        "transparent": true,
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "#73BF69", "value": null },
                { "color": "#FF9830", "value": 500 },
                { "color": "#F2495C", "value": 2000 }
              ]
            },
            "unit": "ms", "decimals": 0,
            "mappings": [{ "type": "special", "options": { "match": "null", "result": { "text": "No data" } } }]
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "auto",
          "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Unique Operations (span types)",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 1 },
        "transparent": true,
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "count(sum by (span_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])) > 0)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
            "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "#8AB8FF", "value": null }] },
            "unit": "short", "decimals": 0
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none",
          "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "auto",
          "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
        }
      },

      {
        "collapsed": false,
        "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
        "id": 200,
        "title": "⏱️ Latency Analysis by Operation",
        "type": "row"
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "P95 Latency by Service (timeseries)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} P95",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le, service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} P99",
            "refId": "B"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 5,
              "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true
            },
            "unit": "ms"
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"] },
          "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "🐢 Top 20 Slowest Operations — P95 (table)",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "topk(20, histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, span_name, service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m]))))",
            "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} | {{span_name}}",
            "refId": "A",
            "instant": true,
            "format": "table"
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          { "id": "organize", "options": {
            "renameByName": { "Value": "P95 Latency (ms)", "span_name": "Operation", "service_name": "Service" },
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "job": true, "le": true, "instance": true }
          }}
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "ms",
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": null },
                { "color": "orange", "value": 500 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 2000 }
              ]
            },
            "custom": {
              "displayMode": "color-background",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Operation" },
              "properties": [
                { "id": "custom.width", "value": 280 },
                { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "auto" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Service" },
              "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 140 }]
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "P95 Latency (ms)", "desc": true }],
          "footer": { "show": false }
        }
      },

      {
        "collapsed": false,
        "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
        "id": 300,
        "title": "🔴 Error Hotspots",
        "type": "row"
      },
      {
        "id": 20,
        "title": "Error Rate Trend by Service (5m)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])) / sum by (service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 15,
              "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true
            },
            "unit": "percent", "min": 0
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"] },
          "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 21,
        "title": "🚨 Top Operations with Errors (table, 5m)",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "topk(15, sum by (span_name, service_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} | {{span_name}}",
            "refId": "A",
            "instant": true,
            "format": "table"
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          { "id": "organize", "options": {
            "renameByName": { "Value": "Error Rate (spans/s)", "span_name": "Operation", "service_name": "Service" },
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "job": true, "instance": true }
          }}
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "custom": {
              "displayMode": "color-background",
              "align": "auto"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": null },
                { "color": "orange", "value": 0.01 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 0.1 }
              ]
            }
          },
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Operation" },
              "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 280 }]
            },
            {
              "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Service" },
              "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 140 }]
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Error Rate (spans/s)", "desc": true }],
          "footer": { "show": false }
        }
      },

      {
        "collapsed": false,
        "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
        "id": 400,
        "title": "📊 Operation Volume & Distribution",
        "type": "row"
      },
      {
        "id": 30,
        "title": "Request Rate by Operation (stacked, top 15)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "topk(15, sum by (span_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{span_name}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "bars", "lineWidth": 0, "fillOpacity": 80,
              "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true,
              "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" }
            },
            "unit": "reqps"
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"] },
          "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
        }
      },

      {
        "collapsed": false,
        "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 34 },
        "id": 500,
        "title": "🔗 DB & Cache Span Analysis",
        "type": "row"
      },
      {
        "id": 40,
        "title": "DB Span Latency P95 (psycopg traces)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 35 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, span_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{span_name=~\".*SELECT.*|.*INSERT.*|.*UPDATE.*|.*DELETE.*|postgresql.*|db\\..*\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{span_name}} P95",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true
            },
            "unit": "ms"
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"] },
          "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 41,
        "title": "Redis / Cache Span Latency P95",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 35 },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, span_name) (rate(otel_traces_span_metrics_duration_milliseconds_bucket{span_name=~\".*redis.*|.*REDIS.*|.*GET|.*SET|.*HGET.*|.*cache.*\"}[5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "{{span_name}} P95",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true
            },
            "unit": "ms"
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"] },
          "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
        }
      },

      {
        "id": 42,
        "title": "💡 How to use Jaeger for trace details",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 43 },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "## 🔗 Xem trace chi tiết trong Jaeger\n\nCác panel trên dùng **spanmetrics** từ Prometheus — cho thấy *thống kê* theo thời gian.\n\nĐể xem **trace cụ thể** (đầy đủ call stack, span cha/con):\n1. Mở [Jaeger UI](http://localhost:16686)\n2. Chọn **Service**: `saleor` hoặc `saleor-worker`\n3. Filter theo **Operation Name** lấy từ bảng \"Slowest Operations\" hoặc \"Error Hotspots\" ở trên\n4. Set **Min Duration** để tìm traces chậm\n\n> **Tip**: Copy span_name từ bảng trên → dán vào field **Operation** của Jaeger để tìm trace tương ứng."
        }
      }

    ]
  },
  "overwrite": true
}
